      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i know i should see a doc but i hate going to the clinics here, its always so crowded and i never want to wait for hours just to be told to take more of what i'm already taking. do u think it could just be my fitness? i havent been as active lately so maybe it's just my lungs getting a bit lazy with age?",
